data.description: This lovely 5/3 home is situated on over 1/3 acre and is ready for new owners. This well maintained home offers beautiful ceramic tile throughout, an amazing tile backsplash in the kitchen, updated fixtures in the bathrooms, ceiling fans throughout, newer a/c (2015), newer roof (2014), new gas pool heater (2020) and a freshly resurfaced pool (2022). Relax under the covered lanai overlooking the south facing solar & gas heated pool & huge backyard with no immediate rear neighbors. Located in the fabulous neighborhood of Greater Groves offering a community pool, playground, basketball, tennis courts and covered picnic area, all situated close to shopping, restaurants, interstates and theme parks. This original owner, turnkey home is ready for new primary residents or investors. HOA fees are included in the property taxes and are not a separate fee. Hurry up and schedule your viewing today! You don't want to miss out on this one!
